to respond to it.

06:04.970 --> 06:07.330
And so it kind of
got me thinking, like,

06:07.330 --> 06:08.900
"Oh, maybe I should
develop this

06:08.900 --> 06:11.770
into a actual trick."
So it took three years

06:11.770 --> 06:14.800
