10:16.730 --> 10:19.670
- Please welcome back
to the "Fool Us" stage,

10:19.670 --> 10:21.800
Kostya Kimlat!

10:21.800 --> 10:24.930
[cheers and applause]

10:24.930 --> 10:26.330
- Thank you!

10:26.330 --> 10:28.530
Thank you very much!
