11:30.970 --> 11:32.530
I have to be clever.
- Oh.

11:32.530 --> 11:34.330
- I have to be sneaky.
- Mm.

11:34.330 --> 11:36.200
- I might even have to lie
just a little.

11:36.200 --> 11:37.200
- [gasps]
- Yeah!

11:37.200 --> 11:38.400
- Shocking.
- I know!

11:38.400 --> 11:40.070
- So I-I'm gonna do
the same trick for them.

