20:09.670 --> 20:14.770
♪ It's not an illusion ♪

20:14.770 --> 20:17.700
♪ Here comes the magic ♪

20:17.700 --> 20:19.530
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:19.530 --> 20:22.070
♪ Whoo-ooh-ooh ♪

20:22.070 --> 20:23.600
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:23.600 --> 20:26.500
♪ Yeah, yeah ♪

20:26.500 --> 20:28.000
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:28.000 --> 20:29.700
Come on!

20:29.700 --> 20:31.230
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:31.230 --> 20:33.600
[cheers and applause]
Thank you!

20:33.600 --> 20:38.330
Rope through the body,
one more time!

20:38.330 --> 20:41.870
Gotta believe in magic.

20:41.870 --> 20:43.670
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:43.670 --> 20:45.830
[cheers and applause]
In your face.

20:45.830 --> 20:47.530
[laughter]

20:47.530 --> 20:49.830
♪ Ooh-ooh-ooh ♪

20:49.830 --> 20:53.170
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:53.170 --> 20:55.100
[laughter]

20:55.100 --> 20:59.470
♪ Yeah, gotta believe
in magic ♪

20:59.470 --> 21:02.330
♪ Whoa-oh ♪

21:02.330 --> 21:04.900
[audience cheering]
♪ Oh, no ♪

21:04.900 --> 21:09.270
♪ Yeah, believe in magic ♪

21:09.270 --> 21:12.430
<i>♪ ♪</i>

21:12.430 --> 21:14.870
Oh, [bleep].
[audience laughter]

21:14.870 --> 21:18.800
<i>♪ ♪</i>

21:18.800 --> 21:21.030
♪ Hello ♪

21:21.030 --> 21:23.200
♪ Can you turn up the music ♪

21:23.200 --> 21:28.830
♪ Believe in magic, yeah ♪

21:28.830 --> 21:31.530
♪ You gotta believe ♪

21:31.530 --> 21:35.370
♪ In magic, oh-oh-oh ♪

